  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Pilot a weaponized hot air balloon through hostile skies.</strong><br><strong>Scavenge, fight and survive against an occult biotech corporation hiding a world ending mistake.   </strong> <br><strong>A stylized action horror game with aerial combat, and survival mechanics.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/0fa402586870791651b69b958e6cbd24.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1560 height=159 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/4a733d124fd706f4079c67367d062e9a.poster.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1170 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/4a733d124fd706f4079c67367d062e9a.webm?t=1774029615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/4a733d124fd706f4079c67367d062e9a.mp4?t=1774029615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Everything you need comes from the world itself or from people who barely survived it.</strong><br><strong>Scrap, metal sheets, gears, and cloth are used to repair damage and improve your flying machine.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/d949ce5c20b1d5a8c7d3ef22144bd4da.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1560 height=159 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/d52613d6f582970b248233ba1bc9a44a.poster.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1170 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/d52613d6f582970b248233ba1bc9a44a.webm?t=1774029615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/d52613d6f582970b248233ba1bc9a44a.mp4?t=1774029615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Use mounted weapons to fight Blinky and when things get too close fight back with an axe or shotgun.</strong><br><strong>Manage limited med kits, and get airborne again before you’re overrun.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/e84fb6761def964b0ac7f8974bc4bdde.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1560 height=159 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/1673a450bfef4d0c61e2f7262bdb1034.poster.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1170 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/1673a450bfef4d0c61e2f7262bdb1034.webm?t=1774029615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/1673a450bfef4d0c61e2f7262bdb1034.mp4?t=1774029615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Quantum Corp’s underground facility is sealed beneath a massive energy dome.</strong><br><strong>The only way in is by powering Tesla Towers spread across the islands.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/ac2fed9a9062b44d98194bc95acecff5.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1560 height=159 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/d3f874c0321ce0be0558cb4c02a688c2.poster.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1170 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/d3f874c0321ce0be0558cb4c02a688c2.webm?t=1774029615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/d3f874c0321ce0be0558cb4c02a688c2.mp4?t=1774029615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Your flying machine isn’t just transport, it’s how the game is built.</strong><br><strong>Take off, fly freely between islands and approach objectives from above.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/ff1d14f3c4fec23ed4cd4f7d251723a0.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1560 height=159 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/60126c66bead491496eb7201ace43f83.poster.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1170 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/60126c66bead491496eb7201ace43f83.webm?t=1774029615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The islands are home to strange survivors with their own problems and ideas.</strong><br><strong>They offer gigs, weapons and materials, usually in exchange for something dangerous or weird.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/be7c3289ba00c033b6d614b5c4b3ec71.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1560 height=159 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Night never really goes away. The skies look wrong.</strong><br><strong>Things are dangerous but they rarely play out the way you expect.  </strong><br><strong>Anything that starts serious usually doesn’t stay that way for long.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
