_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The islands are home to strange survivors with their own problems and ideas.</strong><br><strong>They offer gigs, weapons and materials, usually in exchange for something dangerous or weird.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4305130/extras/be7c3289ba00c033b6d614b5c4b3ec71.avif?t=1774029615\" width=1560 height=159 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Night never really goes away. The skies look wrong.</strong><br><strong>Things are dangerous but they rarely play out the way you expect.  </strong><br><strong>Anything that starts serious usually doesn’t stay that way for long.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
